5e ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Guttschuss presents thirteen </div><div class="t m3de x1e h24 y1bd7 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">powerful stories as evidence. </div><div class="t mad1 x196 h3b y1bd7 ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He </div><div class="t m146f x1e h3b y1c3c ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lives, </div><div class="t mb89 x4b h24 y1c3c ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">an inspiring book from </div><div class="t m22b x1e h24 y1c71 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Pacific Press. </div><div class="t m2e9 x1e h51 y142e ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Available from your ABC or </div><div class="t m7e4 x1e h51 y1425 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by calling 1-800-447-7377. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
